    Ethylene Glycol total: 0.198 / 0.004092
    1,4-Dioxane total: 0.003194 / 0.000066
    Iso Propyl Alcohol total: 80.93 / 1.6725
    tert-Butyl alcohol total: 5.29 / 0.10935
    Heptane total: 5.29 / 0.10935
    Acetone total: 69.89 / 1.44435
    Methanol total: 54.73 / 1.131
    Toluene total: 11.50 / 0.23763
    Drug Product: 3444.39 / 20666.34
- Polysorbate 80 EG shows 620 ppm / 0.004092 from Excel.
- Dehydrated Alcohol shows 275 / 1650 / Methanol 200 ppm / 0.33 from Excel.
- Conclusion definitive: USP <467> Option 2 / ICH Q3C compliance.

